{
  "stem": "13063.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My music involvement at that time was singing during services.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was-- as a matter of fact, my mentor, Cantor Mandelbaum, [NON-ENGLISH], was also in Ghetto Cracow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was also officiating or singing for-- at the services when-- at the-- in the same place where I was attending, the same room.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He used to come there often and sing for us and officiate and lead the services.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this was my only exposure in the ghetto to music-- singing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Social life in ghetto?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "None whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Fun?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, of course not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Were people getting married at all?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very, very few, very few, very few.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was almost-- it was an event of-- of-- of-- of exception, I would say, to get married in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very rare.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I heard of somebody getting married, but--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do not-- I do not remember attending a bris or-- or anything in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, no, no, no, no, no, I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because who would want to bring a child to a-- to a world that was so fraught with uncertainty, where there was no future?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whoever would want this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Although we, as I said before, we-- our lives, we did not feel that our very lives were yet threatened, but we did not know how we would get out of all this misery in the ghetto and-- while the Germans had such a-- still such tremendous power over us and-- and in-- in general in Poland.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This I saw only in the-- in the-- in the Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, in Plaszow camp, this I saw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were really two streets-- two main streets in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
